description:
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic Registered Nurse to join our nursing team in providing care and support to patients and their families whilst undergoing specific cardiac diagnostic / interventional procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require a Registered Nurse with experience working within Cardiology and/or the Catheter Lab, with highly developed communication skills to work within our established multidisciplinary team. You should have evidence of continued professional development including a minimum of intermediate life support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an individual who is hard working, positive, friendly, approachable and ultimately committed to providing high quality standards of holistic care. You would need to work flexibly within the demands of the units work load.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mel Bulgin - Department Leader/Cardiology Head of Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: m.bulgin@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01623 622515 ext 6293&lt;/p&gt;
